/**
 * Test user profile update with various input validation errors.
 * 
 * This test focuses on validating the input validation system by attempting
 * to update a user profile with invalid data. The test follows a complete
 * user journey:
 * 1. Register a new user account with valid credentials
 * 2. Authenticate the user to obtain a JWT token
 * 3. Attempt to update the user profile with invalid data
 * 4. Verify the system properly rejects invalid inputs with appropriate errors
 * 
