 * 
 * This test validates that the API properly handles invalid search criteria by attempting
 * to retrieve todo list channels with malformed parameters. The test follows the complete
 * user journey from account creation through authentication and token validation before
 * testing error conditions.
 * 
 * The ITodoListChannel.IRequest DTO includes filtering by name, description, and
 * date ranges (created_at_from, created_at_to, updated_at_from, updated_at_to),
 * all of which are expected to follow ISO 8601 date-time format. This test verifies
 * that providing invalid date-time formats triggers appropriate validation errors.
 * 
